text: Sergey Omelchenko (born 16 February 1953) is a Soviet skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
